@@JvCsvParse.pas
Summary
  The Unit JvCsvParse is a library of Pascal PChar buffer, and Pascal String handling functions. They
  are used by TJvCsvDataSet. They are also generally useful to any component which needs to parse
  semantic information in a file, and are useful for parsing CSV, XML, or any other structured textual
  file format which you may encounter.

  See also TJvCsvDataSet.
